        "TextSection": {
            "TextSectionType": "Definition",
            "Contents": "A rare leukodystrophy characterized by congenital thickened wrinkled skin showing loss of elasticity in combination with childhood onset of rapidly progressive generalized cognitive and motor impairment quickly resulting in a vegetative state and early death. Neuropathologic examination reveals neuroaxonal leukodystrophy with numerous neuroaxonal spheroids and diffuse loss of axons and myelin sheaths."
        },
